      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 116: applyIncrease() divides by cfg_.increaseRampTime without validating that the config value is positive. Config is public and the constructor accepts caller-provided values, so a zero or negative ramp time can produce inf/NaN ramp progress and unstable bitrate decisions. Validate Config in the constructor or guard the denominator before division.\n```suggestion\n        const auto rampTime \u003d std::max(cfg_.increaseRampTime, 0.001f);\n        rampProgress \u003d std::clamp((secSinceDecrease - cfg_.probeDelaySec) / rampTime, 0.0f, 1.0f);\n```",
